### Test 1: Happy path
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/classify?name=james

###

### Test 2: Missing name — expect 400
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/classify

###

### Test 3: Empty name — expect 400
GET http://127.0.0.1:8001/api/classify?name=

###

### Test 4: Array param (non-string) — expect 422
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/classify?name[]=john&name[]=jane

###

### Test 5: Name with no gender data — expect 200 + error body
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/classify?name=xyzabc123

###

### Test 6: Check CORS header is present
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/classify?name=maria
